{"tid":1388970,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"《騎乘之王》","createTime":"2019-07-30T19:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T19:53:51.000Z","uid":78143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6837f62609da94106daf9daada86846ab43b64a9","tid":1388970,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:53:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.tongli.com.tw/webpages/book/KD1561001/book.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tongli.com.tw%2Fwebpages%2Fbook%2FKD1561001%2Fbook.png&h=1a556807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中亞小國普魯吉亞的終身總統亞歷桑德‧普魯契諾夫，是一位帶領國家贏得獨立的偉大領袖。 <br />\n不過勤於政事的他，其實一直很想找到新的「騎乘物」來滿足自己的「騎乘欲」。<br />\n某天，普魯契諾夫遭到恐怖份子攻擊，他成功擋下攻擊，不料卻被斷裂的雕像頭部重壓導致昏迷。<br />\n而等他再次醒來，竟然已經來到一個完全陌生的世界，各種前所未見的生物正在等待著他&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}